@d4 1
a4 1
<TITLE>The Gran Turismo Pit Stop - Arcade - Extras</TITLE>
d13 1
a13 1
Arcade - Extras
d19 3
a21 3
<BR><BR>
<HR>
<BR>
d23 7
a29 13
<OL>
  <LI> Win each of the arcade tracks with all 3 classes of cars.  (A, B & C)
	Doing so on each track opens up an extra track.  The 4 tracks are:
	Autumn Ring, Deep Forest, Special Stage R5 & Grand Valley.
  <LI> Win each of the extra arcade tracks with all 3 classes of cars.
	Doing so on each extra track unlocks a different manufacturer.
	The 4 manufacturers are: Subaru, Dodge, Toyota & TVR.
  <LI> By winning all 8 tracks using all 3 classes of cars on the Normal
	level, the staff credit movie is displayed.  This is now also
	accessible from the menus.
  <LI> By winning all 8 tracks using all 3 classes of cars on the Difficult
	level, the "GT Hi-Res" mode is accessible from the menus. 
</OL>
